\": \"recent mishaps\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1743}, {\"ngram\": \"sewer problems\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Without the Games, I would have needed an extra 10 years\\\" to make these transformations, she said.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"an extra 10 years\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"these transformations\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it (preparing for the Olympics) was clearly an acceleration of the transformation of Paris, of the ecological transformation of Paris in terms of mobility, of swimming in the Seine, which I would not have been able to do on such a scale, at such a pace, if it had not been for the Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2087075392992136e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2004, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2087075392992136e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999577085, \"rank\": 4.234690896983586e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"an acceleration\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"the transformation\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecological transfor